data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN at 3.75%. Nestled in the heart of Loudoun wine country, this charming home offers the best of Northern Virginia living. Designed with both comfort and tranquility in mind, this stunning residence is situated in the highly sought-after Village Green community. The timeless brick-front exterior welcomes you with a charming front porch and panoramic mountain views, creating an ideal setting for a serene lifestyle. Upon entering, hardwood floors grace the main level, seamlessly connecting formal living and dining areas to the open-concept family room and eat-in kitchen, complete with granite countertops and stainless appliances. With five bedrooms, 4 full baths, and an impressive primary suite featuring a walk-in closet and spa-like-en-suite bath, this home seamlessly blends luxury and comfort. The Village Green community, surrounded by conservation land, offers amenities such as tennis and basketball courts, a clubhouse with pools, and playgrounds, providing a rural escape with modern conveniences. Easy access to Route 15 and the MARC Station makes exploring nearby breweries, vineyards, and historic sites a breeze, offering a swift commute to Washington, DC. This residence perfectly harmonizes convenience with rural charm-an unmissable opportunity for those seeking the best of both worlds.
